            "code_var_name": "cal_T_tensile_stress",
            "description": "The tensile pre-stress load per unit surface area, represented in script form in the weak formulation.\nJUSTIFICATION:\nThe symbol 'T' in script form (mathvariant='script') appears in the weak form and is used in the same context as the regular 'T', indicating it is the same tensile stress variable, just represented in a different notation.",
