            "code_var_name": "d_Gamma_interface",
            "description": "The differential element of the interface \u0393, used in surface integrals over boundaries.\nJUSTIFICATION:\nThe symbol 'd\u0393' appears in integrals over the interface \u0393, such as in the transmission conditions, and denotes the surface element for integration.",
